::Aerotaur::
       He grunts.  "Figures he'd send you.  Just my luck."  He stands still 
for a moment with his hands on his hips.  "No, she's better off with the 
Predacons anyway.  At least you know they might shoot you in the back."  He 
turns around showing the scorch marks on his back.  "First they shoot me, 
then they let you keep Nightlight.  I say to the pit with them all.  So I've 
decided to join up.  At least this way I can keep her safe."

--part1_1da.7742abf.2bcc618b_boundary
